HEADWORD: Impedimental
<hw>Im*ped`i*men"tal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of the nature
of an impediment; hindering; obstructing; impeditive.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Things so <qex>impedimental</qex> to success.</q> <rj><qau>G. H.
Lewes.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Impedite</ent>⟦br⟧
